    "about": "Unetix is an AI-powered analytics platform that unifies fragmented payment data across multiple providers into a single independent intelligence solution. The platform connects merchants to all their acquirers, PSPs, orchestrators, payment methods and third-party providers — with 200+ pre-built connectors. Unetix operates on a no-code integration model, going operational within 30 minutes.",
