    "about": "Scoutd AI is a football scouting platform that combines a global player database with a proprietary football-native language model. It covers players across multiple leagues with detailed performance metrics — technical skills, physical data, tactical awareness, movement analysis — presented as percentile rankings against peers, essentially turning real-life players into stat sheets comparable to FIFA player cards.",
